      "utilityType": "control",
      "description": "Choose one visible object within 60 feet that blocks access, such as a door, box, chest, manacles, padlock, or similar mundane or magical closure; one mundane lock, stuck state, or barred state becomes unlocked, unstuck, or unbarred, only one lock opens if there are multiple, Arcane Lock is suppressed for 10 minutes instead, and a loud knock is audible from up to 300 feet from the target.",
